{"tid":1281172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[老解] 想講少少關於 \"駐港解放軍\"","createTime":"2019-07-03T08:14:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T12:07:43.000Z","uid":271241,"like":162,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"7399a41392247e25e60cc1482942d4621f9afcdf","tid":1281172,"uid":271241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:14:19.000Z","msg":"見次次一有衝突都有人話會出老解，<br />\n政治因素唔太了解，少少見聞分享。<br />\n<br />\n機緣巧合下，幾年前喺其中一個軍營工作過（工程撚，勿起底）。就個人觀察/同啲兵仔交談，有以下幾點想分享：<br />\n<br />\n- 駐港部隊大多為新兵<br />\n同一個負責聯絡嘅兵仔好多接觸，佢喺大陸高中畢業就嚟當兵，會留喺香港駐軍兩年，之後就退役返大陸。成日喺佢面前屌大陸佬共產黨，佢好撚無奈。聽佢講同我個人觀察，駐港部隊多數都係後生仔、新兵，有軍階嗰啲都係有人脈先嚟到香港做，因為係悠位嚟，我接觸過軍營第二把膠椅，佢都係好撚hea，日日唔係飲酒就瞓。曾經有廣州軍區高層嚟過audit, 對我哋工程佬都好撚客氣，感覺似狗隊 PPRB 搞關係咁。<br />\n<br />\n- 佔中前，軍隊有相關演練<br />\n班駐軍平時都會操下體能，例如孭鐵跑圈，過障礙物等等。但佔中前，見過佢哋有針對做人群管制訓練，但好撚hea, 搵幾十條友扮示威者鳩叫，然後又擺幾架裝甲車開咪勸喻咁。唔知係真心準備，定做畀我哋/ 附近民居睇。當然，基本軍隊嘅軍備例如坦克，裝甲車，通訊/信號干擾車，佢哋都有啦。<br />\n<br />\n- 軍隊可隨意出入境，無需清關<br />\n呢樣我諗好多人都知。兵仔話，佢哋退役返鄉下之前，會放假出去鳩嗚，去尖沙咀買下金呀奶粉嗰啲 19 嘢，啲野隊晒上軍車半夜一嘢車返大陸。<br />\n<br />\n純粹分享下所見所聞，唔係叫大家掉以輕心，只係唔想因為對某啲嘢唔了解，就被呢類白色恐怖影響。"},{"pid":"42272ec126821a8be1301cbbb43f27ae0e2b33a5","tid":1281172,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:22:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eea3a6cee1429a097d5f8debb4664aa9a65ce3cb","tid":1281172,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:29:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc8e954b2ead861589cadb43d52d41183c554ff0","tid":1281172,"uid":177089,"like":56,"dislike":0,"score":56,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:31:30.000Z","msg":"如果真係出老解 就係其他軍區派入嚟 <br />\n駐紮部隊係必要時頂住 但香港本身有警隊呢個武裝單位<br />\n<br />\n所以無論駐港部隊幾廢都無用 佢地無論咩情況都係唔會出嚟"},{"pid":"5b1df131bb36bdb6d7099b7caaa1759aab3800cc","tid":1281172,"uid":24140,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:34:25.000Z","msg":"支那無咁易出老解<br />\n港驚連實彈都未出<br />\n<br />\n好多人+支畜五毛嚇大家"},{"pid":"ca6e6d7aec826c50477622a6f7e8a8077fcaa15d","tid":1281172,"uid":147233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:35:47.000Z","msg":"想問下d兵係咩省人 識唔識廣東話？<br />\n到時叫救命驚唔識聽"},{"pid":"5384413292d203a29ffe4a775c9242803dbb57c2","tid":1281172,"uid":271241,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ca6e6d7aec826c50477622a6f7e8a8077fcaa15d","tid":1281172,"uid":147233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:35:47.000Z","msg":"想問下d兵係咩省人 識唔識廣東話？<br />\n到時叫救命驚唔識聽"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:42:01.000Z","msg":"我接觸幾個兵仔同隊長都識廣東話，亦有啲外省樣講普通話。"},{"pid":"be22d2350f95fc62407c7f6c4076cbafaaed22fb","tid":1281172,"uid":78769,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:44:09.000Z","msg":"乜駐港解放軍有坦克車咩？<br />\n唔係頂多裝甲車？"},{"pid":"a9000c93ec275c983aabb5674db396637373487c","tid":1281172,"uid":271857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:46:07.000Z","msg":"當年解放軍都係攞把刀去繳械再打"},{"pid":"63308144834a8444d132eb0c24f63ac71d07516a","tid":1281172,"uid":193436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:54:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b28d042cf3d5bbd7f1653a88fffc005facfb895d","tid":1281172,"uid":271241,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"bc8e954b2ead861589cadb43d52d41183c554ff0","tid":1281172,"uid":177089,"like":56,"dislike":0,"score":56,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:31:30.000Z","msg":"如果真係出老解 就係其他軍區派入嚟 <br />\n駐紮部隊係必要時頂住 但香港本身有警隊呢個武裝單位<br />\n<br />\n所以無論駐港部隊幾廢都無用 佢地無論咩情況都係唔會出嚟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:54:21.000Z","msg":"都係，深圳部隊落嚟都好快，又港豬澳又高鐵..."},{"pid":"5a88496a8aed39bf5e6815679f0b7fb665917030","tid":1281172,"uid":36120,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5384413292d203a29ffe4a775c9242803dbb57c2","tid":1281172,"uid":271241,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ca6e6d7aec826c50477622a6f7e8a8077fcaa15d","tid":1281172,"uid":147233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:35:47.000Z","msg":"想問下d兵係咩省人 識唔識廣東話？<br />\n到時叫救命驚唔識聽"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:42:01.000Z","msg":"我接觸幾個兵仔同隊長都識廣東話，亦有啲外省樣講普通話。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:54:24.000Z","msg":"記得 97 前後咁上下外國傳媒採訪過駐港解放軍，話有 CBT 教佢地用廣東話、英文對一般市民宣佈命令"},{"pid":"644e84f0de8ee018b6d9b9ae0e61782417d1bf27","tid":1281172,"uid":9230,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:04:56.000Z","msg":"駐港澳部隊嘅兵全部揀過，都係城市兵（即係城市戶口讀書，有高中畢業嘅） 論文化仲好過班毅進仔<br />\n<br />\n軍官全部都係國防大學或者一本重點大學畢業。"},{"pid":"238770a918ece44164f30b73ebf46f17278171d2","tid":1281172,"uid":202348,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:15:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40f5721734c5ec1887cb6f6b19f2a8177807f627","tid":1281172,"uid":39812,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:22:34.000Z","msg":"如果香港真係出老解一定係其他軍區落來<br />\n當年六四屠城落手嘅亦都係其他軍區派調入去鎮壓 本身駐守北京好多掉返轉同情學生冇落手之後要逃亡"},{"pid":"03bd2d031a3f417831e15a1cd5590016812bef55","tid":1281172,"uid":198175,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:24:02.000Z","msg":"各省有武警獨立的專業防暴隊專門鎮壓暴亂, 並不統屬於縣市, 以防地方政府濫用, 當地方發生暴亂時, 而地方公安無法壓制, 才會要求省政府派出武警防暴隊, 例如2014年茂名PX廠, 再之前的重慶萬州暴動...<br />\n<br />\n當地方要求上級出動武警防暴隊, 地方財政是要向武警支付出警費用, 以及會在地方官員的個人政績上留有黑紀錄, 是故如無必要, 地方政府都不想搞出大規模動亂要出動武警收拾殘局.<br />\n<br />\n至於香港因為所謂一國兩制, 只能動用駐港部隊, 按理應不可隨便動用廣東武警或其他部隊來港.<br />\n<br />\n不過落嚟鎮壓係乜部隊, 只要換件衫換個番號就得, 連蓄龍都識玩black bloc, 你點知D無編號的黑衫人係乜水."},{"pid":"87662107b7b85f7a15980a4fca20b6a64d7c3a69","tid":1281172,"uid":271241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:03:29.000Z","msg":"有冇參觀過軍營嘅手足分享下"},{"pid":"4a5fd78ad829b4e122b7e758038550d51ac132da","tid":1281172,"uid":271241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:45:26.000Z","msg":"又有人講坦克，我又推下先"},{"pid":"f5ba2190ab1898a6e630bd5490589fe371771c8d","tid":1281172,"uid":69013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:59:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bc0a4a7e2f091c4ff8461deb523b2340f260fac","tid":1281172,"uid":26283,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"bc8e954b2ead861589cadb43d52d41183c554ff0","tid":1281172,"uid":177089,"like":56,"dislike":0,"score":56,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:31:30.000Z","msg":"如果真係出老解 就係其他軍區派入嚟 <br />\n駐紮部隊係必要時頂住 但香港本身有警隊呢個武裝單位<br />\n<br />\n所以無論駐港部隊幾廢都無用 佢地無論咩情況都係唔會出嚟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T12:06:15.000Z","msg":"六四時係專登係北京外面軍區<br />\n搵啲唔識字既農民兵洗佢地腦推入去屠城<br />\n而唔會用北京本地軍<br />\n<br />\n好多讀過下書有文化既軍人係抗命唔願殺學生<br />\n最出名係徐勤先講<br />\n寧願殺頭也不能做歷史的罪人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而趙紫陽坐到總理+總書記<br />\n為左救學生比人軟禁至死<br />\n有良心開明既大陸人成代係六四果時比人清洗曬<br />\n<br />\n之後幾十年就係養愚民同憤青去頂著<br />\n真正覺醒左有讀書既好多都會移民<br />\n所以上面就係得返啲比人洗腦既係道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afc25e9f95a00efa089c73af62356da9efe755df","tid":1281172,"uid":271241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5ba2190ab1898a6e630bd5490589fe371771c8d","tid":1281172,"uid":69013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:59:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T12:06:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"647736014bf3cca8d8e0608f5e6b75e78551c718","tid":1281172,"uid":72228,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"afc25e9f95a00efa089c73af62356da9efe755df","tid":1281172,"uid":271241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5ba2190ab1898a6e630bd5490589fe371771c8d","tid":1281172,"uid":69013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:59:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T12:06:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T12:09:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c9c180c229d0b04395c95e333e8820d643e0820","tid":1281172,"uid":26283,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"40f5721734c5ec1887cb6f6b19f2a8177807f627","tid":1281172,"uid":39812,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:22:34.000Z","msg":"如果香港真係出老解一定係其他軍區落來<br />\n當年六四屠城落手嘅亦都係其他軍區派調入去鎮壓 本身駐守北京好多掉返轉同情學生冇落手之後要逃亡"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T12:10:12.000Z","msg":"所以唔明香港警察 特別係白衫以上<br />\n點都叫讀過下書<br />\n點解可以對本地自己人開槍<br />\n真係大陸人都不如<br />\n藍衫二皮幾白衫四皮幾<br />\n一車車良心賣比港共<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7e3f09ffa17477157a02bca603a4b560aa75f8a","tid":1281172,"uid":163916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T12:11:56.000Z","msg":"電子戰"},{"pid":"3de878064d25707c59ba99f55f9a0a18ee23fb2c","tid":1281172,"uid":42396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T12:14:30.000Z","msg":"係咪真係得幾舊水一個月？"}]}